---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-900/90 via-primary-800/80 to-primary-700/70 mix-blend-multiply z-10"></div>
    <img 
      src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5905498/pexels-photo-5905498.jpeg" 
      alt="Personas leyendo la Biblia juntas" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover transform scale-105 animate-zoom-slow"
    />
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight animate-fade-in">
        Traduciendo las Escrituras.<br />
        <span class="text-accent-400">Transformando Vidas.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up animation-delay-200">
        Empoderando comunidades alrededor del mundo con la Palabra de Dios en su idioma materno, construyendo iglesias maduras que transforman comunidades.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6 animate-slide-up animation-delay-300">
        <a href="#projects" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-50 font-semibold py-4 px-10 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg">
          Nuestros Proyectos
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#get-involved" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-primary-900 font-semibold py-4 px-10 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg">
          Invol√∫crate
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-20 animate-bounce-slow">
    <a href="#about" aria-label="Desplazarse hacia abajo" class="group">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white/80 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes zoom-slow {
    0% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }
  
  .animate-zoom-slow {
    animation: zoom-slow 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  
  .animate-bounce-slow {
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }
</style>